title: Inflation rate in Germany 1992 to 2019
summary: The chart at hand is a line chart where the x axis denotes Year and a y axis denotes Year-on-year change. In total the number of data points it has is 28.
Overall Year-on-year change has decreased over the Year.
The steepest increase occurs in between the Year '19 and '92.
Maximum Year-on-year change, about 5.1 was reported at Year '92
The lowest Year-on-year change, of value 0.3 was reported at Year '09
